1.title: Carnivores vs. Veggies
1.plot: The veggies take on the carnivores in this episode of Compete to Eat. On Muskoka's sparkling Six Mile Lake, Chef Jo cooks up some meat magic with a bleary-eyed Pete while Chef Aldo finds his inner vegetarian with bacon-hating Katie. Each team has one hour to create a three course meal using only the ingredients and the tools they can find in the cottage. Their gourmet creations are served to family and friends who pick the winner. Can Aldo's quinoa salad with squid steaks squash Jo's chorizo topped tostadas? 2.title: Big Brother vs. Little Sister
2.plot: It's a sibling smackdown in this episode of Compete to Eat when Chefs Jo & Aldo cook with competitive brother Dennis and his sister Jackie in side by side cottages on Lake Muskoka to create a three course gourmet meal in just one hour using only the ingredients and tools they find at each cottage. Will the judging panel of friends and family be swayed by Chef Jo's fried goat cheese salad with cranberry vinaigrette and doughnut bread pudding with peanut butter and jam with chocolate sauce or will Chef Aldo's fennel crusted pork with roasted vegetables and profiteroles ...

3.title: Big City Girl vs. Mamma and Mammoni
3.plot: This week on Compete to Eat, Parry Sound becomes a culinary battleground as Chef Jo works with A-type city girl Samara while Chef Aldo cooks with Italian mother Mary Lou, to create a three-course meal in just one hour using only the ingredients and tools they find at the cottages. Can Chef Jo win over the judging panel of friends and family with her prosciutto wrapped feta-stuffed dates and a boozy parfait with berries and homemade coffee cake or will Chef Aldo blow them away with his butter poached lobster with pickled beets and a strawberry zabaglione?

imdb.title: Compete to Eat
plot: Watch Chef Aldo and Chef Jo travel across cottage country and get paired up with cottagers who may...or may not be gourmet cooks in the kitchen. See how nothing gets in the way of a good meal when Chef Jo and Aldo _Compete to Eat_ (qv).::Morgan Leech
